6
00:00:29,890 --> 00:00:32,370
then you are going to be put in a worse position.

7
00:00:32,370 --> 00:00:36,180
Someone raised an issue about you during our meeting.

8
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:39,060
That's why the director gave that order.

9
00:00:40,160 --> 00:00:44,140
Was it Seo In Woo that had an issue with me?

10
00:00:44,810 --> 00:00:48,850
I think he seems to know something about your arm.

11
00:00:58,790 --> 00:01:01,430
- Na Yeong Joo.
- Yes?

12
00:01:07,660 --> 00:01:09,020
Na Yeong Joo.

13
00:01:09,850 --> 00:01:11,450
Sunbaenim.

14
00:01:12,660 --> 00:01:15,860
- What are you doing here?
- I was leaving for my shift.

15
00:01:15,860 --> 00:01:17,600
Let's go.

16
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:53,610
Turn around, this way is blocked.

17
00:01:53,610 --> 00:01:55,850
Ah yes.

18
00:01:57,840 --> 00:02:00,580
Huh? Manager Park?

19
00:02:00,580 --> 00:02:02,250
Oh! Hi!

20
00:02:02,250 --> 00:02:04,950
Manager Seo and Manager Kim are here, too.

21
00:02:04,950 --> 00:02:08,650
Oh! How have you been? Glad to see you!

22
00:02:08,650 --> 00:02:11,280
Hi!

23
00:02:12,370 --> 00:02:14,670
Ms. Han! Nice to see you.

24
00:02:14,670 --> 00:02:18,930
- Hurry take a look at her. You look great!
-You're really pretty, Ms. Han.

25
00:02:18,930 --> 00:02:21,750
