252
00:23:13,460 --> 00:23:16,180
You really don't know?

253
00:23:16,180 --> 00:23:20,000
If I find out whose it is, I'll just ... !

254
00:23:20,710 --> 00:23:23,560
Excuse me, Section Chief.

255
00:23:24,400 --> 00:23:26,630
What is it?

256
00:23:29,020 --> 00:23:32,690
What is it? Why are you raising your hand?

257
00:23:32,690 --> 00:23:34,980
